Dataset: Motor Vehicle Collisions – Crashes

Source: NYC Open Data

Link:
https://data.cityofnewyork.us/Public-Safety/Motor-Vehicle-Collisions-Crashes/h9gi-nx95

Description:
This dataset contains detailed records of motor vehicle collisions reported in New York City.
Each row represents a single crash event including information about the location,
time, injuries, fatalities, vehicles involved, and contributing factors.
